:"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://flowzilla.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"flowzilla","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"flowzilla","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://flowzilla.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"flowzilla","ctime_ts":1369902183,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/59421116/9682409","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324891.html?thread=17760027#t17760027","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324891.html?thread=17760027#t17760027","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324891.html?thread=17760027#t17760027","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"werthead","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":17760027,"talkid":69375,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324891.html?thread=17760027#t17760027","upictitle":"werthead: SunsetPyrynees","article":"Very say news. THE DYING EARTH had an impact on the fantasy genre that is unparalleled, and the one-volume version of LYONESSE may be the greatest one-volume fantasy book of all time aside from LORD OF THE RINGS. I really need to read more of his stuff, particularly DEMON PRINCES which I've heard many good things about.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"May 30 2013, 09:17:20 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://werthead.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"werthead",